{"type": "article", "id": 24672, "title": "带皲裂纹瓷杯", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-30T07:01:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 31, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122610wG8213APNOJ5HUnh.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这组略带皲裂和分层花纹的瓷杯来自是荷兰设计师 Floris Wubben ，他在一次意外中发现了做出这种纹理的方法，将未干燥的瓷器和瓦斯的火焰接触，而随着两者之间的距离和速度的改变也影响了温度，使瓷杯本身产生更多样的变化。这套瓷杯瓷碗都是基于此方法做出的，有些偶然和手工的痕迹。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122608u1UFoqLVisx5TrgX.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122608DkPioQzmTyUuJje7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122609Rb3wSo79iFOkmjCs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122609inCgmuh9LUy0VASk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}